data.description: Welcome to your opportunity to restore and rejuvenate this charming 3 bedroom 1.5 bathroom home. Nestled in a quiet neighborhood it offers a unique chance for investment or for the first-time homebuyer with a vision. This property exudes character and awaits someone willing to give it some TLC. It sits on a 7553 sq ft lot, providing opportunities for expansion, landscaping, or the addition of outdoor living spaces. Imagine transforming the backyard into a serene oasis or a vibrant garden retreat. This home represents an excellent investment opportunity. With some elbow grease and a touch of creativity, you can turn this house into a personalized home or a lucrative resale.
